OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Facross Cumbria to begin Thursday
OL,7,Fevening, but outbreaks of rain and
OL,8,Fdrizzle soon spreading northwards
OL,9,Facross the region, locally heavy over
OL,10,Fthe hills. Briefly drier during the
OL,11,Fearly hours of Friday, though turning
OL,12,Fbreezier. A mild night.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA band of heavier rain sweeps
OL,15,Feastwards throughout the morning.
OL,16,FTurning brighter into the afternoon
OL,17,Fwith a mix of sunshine and a few
OL,18,Fshowers. Blustery, especially near the
OL,19,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
