OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers continuing Saturday before
OL,7,Fhigh pressure builds giving a largely
OL,8,Fdry and bright Sunday. Perhaps more
OL,9,Fcloud around on Monday with a few
OL,10,Fdrizzly showers over the Pennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
